    "Perhaps the most comprehensive work involved an algorithmic pipeline called \"CathAI\" that was trained on 13,843 studies spanning 5 years of data.",
    "They achieved an AUC of 0.862 (95% CI: 0.843-0.880) 5.",
    "CathAI, while a state-of-the-art pipeline, had several limitations, notably its reliance on static images rather than video data.",
    "This approach may overlook crucial temporal information, which is essential for accurate diagnosis.",
